<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Request Submitted - SID Clinic</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/js/all.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grid)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            height: 90px;
            border-radius: 5%;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 45px 35px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }
        
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 100%);
            color: #92400e;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
        }
        
        .appointment-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.08);
        }
        
        .appointment-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        }
        
        .appointment-card h3 {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #235f8b;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
        .appointment-id {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .info-section h4 {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .info-list li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .info-list li i {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-top: 2px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .important-notes {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .important-notes h4 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.4);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 35px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer h3 {
            color: #60a5fa;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
        }
        
        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .contact-item i {
            color: #60a5fa;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .disclaimer {
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .container {
                border-radius: 12px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 8px;
                padding: 12px 0;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .contact-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>Appointment Request Submitted</h1>
                <p>Your appointment request has been successfully received and is being processed</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Dear {{patientName}},</div>
            
            <p class="intro-text">Thank you for choosing <strong>SID Clinic</strong> for your healthcare needs. Your appointment request has been successfully submitted and is currently under review by our medical team.</p>
            
            <div class="status-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                Pending Confirmation
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-card">
                <h3>
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
                    Appointment Details
                </h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
                        Doctor
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">Dr. {{doctorName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                        Date
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                        Time
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i>
                        Appointment Type
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-id">
                    <i class="fas fa-hashtag"></i>
                    Reference ID: {{appointmentId}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <h4>
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                    Next Steps
                </h4>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                        Dr. {{doctorName}} will review your appointment request within 24 hours
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope-check"></i>
                        You will receive a confirmation email once your appointment is approved
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-file-medical"></i>
                        Any pre-appointment instructions will be provided upon confirmation
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                        Track your appointment status through your patient dashboard
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="important-notes">
                <h4>
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                    Important Guidelines
                </h4>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                        Please arrive 15 minutes before your scheduled appointment time
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i>
                        Bring any relevant medical documents, insurance cards, and test results
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-times"></i>
                        For rescheduling requests, please provide at least 24 hours advance notice
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-id-card"></i>
                        Valid photo identification is required for all appointments
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">
                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                    View Appointment Status
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
                For any questions or assistance regarding your appointment, please contact our patient support team using the information below.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <h3>
                <i class="fas fa-hospital"></i>
                SID Clinic
            </h3>
            <p>Committed to providing exceptional healthcare services with professionalism, compassion, and clinical excellence.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    <span>Office@sidclinic.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                    <span>9274557987</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                    <span>www.sidclinic.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    <span>Visit Our Location</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disclaimer">
                This is an automated notification. Please do not reply directly to this email.
                For assistance, please use our official contact channels listed above.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>